The paper also discusses the European Union's General Data Protection Regulation, which relates to data privacy and security, suggesting that the paper may also belong to the cs.CR sub-category. The use of ASP in various domains, including medicine, cryptography, and biology, suggests that the paper may also belong to the cs.DB sub-category. The paper also discusses explanation approaches, which may involve natural language processing and argumentation, suggesting that the paper may also belong to the cs.CL and cs.LG sub-categories.
